1- Create virtual environment 'VRPD': 
python -m venv VRPD

2- Activate the environment: 
.\VRPD\Scripts\activate

3- install ipykernel: 
pip install ipykernel

4- install virtual environment in kernel:
python -m ipykernel install --name=VRPD

5- associate project to virtual environment:
manually select 'VRPD' kernel